snippet.title: Amber Heard’s Lawyer Accuses Johnny Depp Of Planting Story || Desperate Attempt || Smear Name #story
snippet.description:

A report that surfaced on Thursday (7 January) claimed the Pirates of the Caribbean star, 57, was accusing Heard, 34, of keeping her $7m (£5.1m) divorce settlement. However, Heard’s US lawyer Elaine Bredehoft accused Depp of “planting” the Daily Mail  story while also acknowledging the Aquaman star has been “delayed” in her “goal” to fulfil her original pledge.
